title: Healthcare tech platform Doctolib reaches $6.4 billion valuation - TechCrunch
content: Healthcare tech platform Doctolib reaches $6.4 billion valuation  TechCrunch
description: French startup Doctolib has announced that is has raised a new funding round. With this round, the company has reached a valuation of €5.8 billion, or $6.4 billion at today’s exchange rate. That makes Doctolib the highest valued French startup.
